snippet.title: How to Graph Arctan (tangent inverse)
snippet.description:
Learn how to graph arctan (tangent inverse) in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.

0:13 Graph of the Parent Graph Tangent
0:50 Restrict the Domain so that it has an Inverse
1:12 How to Graph the Inverse by Interchanging the x's and y's
2:30 How to Graph the Asymptotes
